Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.60,0:00:22.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照路顶呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.89,0:00:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说会丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.77,0:00:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有两面性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然鸣人能使用九尾查克拉模式了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.07,0:00:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但并不代表他和九尾搞好了关系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:38.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人的查克拉仍然会被九尾吸走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦查克拉清零 鸣人就会死…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:46.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人此刻很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止激情太过分
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.17,0:00:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用九尾查克拉当手电筒确实不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟丢了 跟紧了 蜂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.32,0:01:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:21.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是毫不客气地消费我的查克拉啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.83,0:01:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在你体内看着你的一举一动呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.85,0:01:30.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.04,0:01:36.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是那么天真
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.72,0:01:41.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这场战争就让我来终结吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.98,0:01:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨也好 痛苦也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部由我来承担
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.71,0:01:53.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了我的查克拉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骨瘦如柴的你变回原样一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.46,0:02:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…还真是少见啊 九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然会主动跟我搭话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你耐不住寂寞想找人倾诉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我现在正忙着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后再听你说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的认为仅凭一己之力就能结束战争吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.78,0:02:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你多少也感觉到敌人的规模有多庞大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.77,0:02:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且斑也在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道他会设下什么圈套哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我就将力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再吃你那套了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.98,0:02:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你变机灵了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.59,0:03:01.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…你早就露出马脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有话战争结束后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.96,0:03:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果同伴被杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仇恨随之便会诞生…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能在事态演变成那样之前消灭所有敌人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.11,0:03:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒敌人就会被他们憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:30.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的想自己背负一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:39.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别总是小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:29.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别总是小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:34.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.95,0:05:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真能消除大家的仇恨并背负一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.08,0:05:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:58.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该出现了很多战死者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时也孕育出了仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.59,0:06:21.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经在你身边的佐助就是为仇恨所困
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对他不是毫无办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.18,0:06:33.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那天起 你就应该察觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会跟谁对战呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是哪个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风帽墨镜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太想和朋友打架
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是那么回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:24.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是传统的忍者对练
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.66,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,历代的火影们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.20,0:07:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是通过忍者对练以提升实力的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.83,0:07:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.41,0:07:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出界了 就算我输吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换后面的继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是训练还是别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.64,0:07:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是为了分个胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.43,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就赶紧决定输赢好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.04,0:07:49.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那么麻烦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙真没志气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一辈子也当不上中忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:07:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 那可不一定
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问为何的话 一生很漫长
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,期间会有很多…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别钻牛角尖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 鹿丸那家伙才是最麻烦的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丁次也毫无斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井野 你认识他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧 父母的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹿丸 丁次 结和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.80,0:08:26.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给忘掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不擅长这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.94,0:08:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也觉得麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经完成和解之印了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.78,0:08:57.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.33,0:08:59.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈不让我跟他说话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.75,0:09:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和他交手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.12,0:09:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后是 宇智波佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩都给我出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.22,0:09:08.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:09.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和佐助结和解之印啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.38,0:09:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助加油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把对手打得落花流水啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙怎么回事 就会装酷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶…打败这个受欢迎的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能备受瞩目了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 我绝对不会输的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油…鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.33,0:09:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就是漩涡鸣人对宇智波佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有本事就来吧 拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.69,0:09:46.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对决前用惯用手和对方结下对立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是礼仪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:50.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种事随便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧让我放倒这家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.20,0:09:56.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在起 我就要人气爆棚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.08,0:09:59.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就如你所愿立刻让你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.50,0:10:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者对练是一直恪守的传统训练方式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有些形式化
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但忍者学校必须从基础教起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.31,0:10:18.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对决之前 一定要单手结印 面向对方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:22.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是双手结印发动忍术动作的一半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示即将进入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是对立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在对决结束 分出胜负之后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方伸出对立之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相互钩在一起 结成和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从而表达出依然是伙伴的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止就是忍者对练的仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.88,0:10:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有在听吗 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.60,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都说第二遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.71,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“好”只要说一次就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.46,0:10:59.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干掉他 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害 好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.04,0:11:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和大家平时看我的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…比那更强烈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.82,0:11:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…他没在看我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.08,0:11:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双方结下和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换下一组
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.14,0:12:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.88,0:12:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就当我不存在吗 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.31,0:12:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对 是狗屎 狗屎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬邦邦稀稀一大坨的混蛋 笨蛋 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.90,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太笨了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙连骂人都不会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是便秘还是拉肚子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望他分清楚些
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问为何的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说别钻牛角尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒说两句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗屎 硬邦邦稀稀一大坨的混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说忍者对练是神圣的传统了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶紧给我结和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.48,0:12:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想打吗 拖后腿的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.84,0:12:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个 适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.31,0:12:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真差劲 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:52.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.99,0:13:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后呢…佐助变成什么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将他的仇恨消除了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.04,0:13:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没有 与此相反
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:37.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该清醒点了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既没有父母 也没有兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.93,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能理解我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.04,0:13:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就孤身一人的你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底能理解我什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.18,0:14:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在无论你说什么 我都不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.90,0:14:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会将你和村里的所有人都杀得一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只有那条路可以走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终你的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.25,0:14:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么杀了我成为守护村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.06,0:14:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要么被我干掉 成为一条丧家之犬
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙的仇恨反而越来越强烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.62,0:14:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身边最亲近的同伴都这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.79,0:14:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 不管是谁…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:53.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都无法消除仇恨 也无法承担仇恨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.47,0:15:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…说完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.61,0:15:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我就该惧怕退缩 无动于衷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不就如你所愿了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真的是你才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连一个佐助都救不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.99,0:15:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么还如此狂妄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果连自己的决定都不相信 那就真完了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会设法帮助佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,设法解决这场战争的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又想封印我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.75,0:16:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是那种小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你寄住在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就给点租金 借些查克拉给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.58,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仙法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.43,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超大玉…螺旋多连丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来最后一击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.60,0:17:00.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这股力量是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…这是九尾的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.86,0:17:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…惹毛我了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这么大的力量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然很厉害啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.12,0:17:54.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是六道的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我记住了 鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当年的小鬼变得相当能说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.42,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.48,0:18:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望有一天也能把你的憎恨给消除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:43.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你让我痛苦不堪…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:49.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我知道被憎恨支配的滋味不好受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.39,0:18:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.20,0:18:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是九尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.11,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没沦落到被你这臭小鬼拯救的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.97,0:19:01.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是憎恨的集合体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.69,0:19:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这反而更有拯救的价值了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:23.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我的确太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但就像老爸老妈曾在我体内一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.12,0:19:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一直与我相伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.74,0:19:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的想法和成长你都能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你也许不愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你一直都在注视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.27,0:19:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…你就继续留在那里关注我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:58.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…你也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:02.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你的眼中从未有过我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我…一直都在关注着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 佐助也好 战争也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都会想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光芒四射的鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,月下严峻的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更加轻松地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.19,0:20:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又和九尾吵架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尾兽模式是和九尾进行的查克拉拔河比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.45,0:20:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有查克拉 生命就落幕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.65,0:20:47.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以别乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.20,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道自己有点乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一向言出必行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.27,0:20:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我的忍道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.21,0:21:04.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要加速了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.80,0:21:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.68,0:22:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经帮你包扎好外伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.88,0:22:54.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你趁现在好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.47,0:22:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.40,0:22:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说医疗忍者接二连三被人暗杀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.17,0:23:02.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宁次.... 怪不得你会如此消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为看不见的敌人不知道隐藏在何处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.45,0:23:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集的火影疾风传是 被狙击的医疗忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 必须要小心了
